<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="raise" id="raise">raise</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
语法：
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;csignal&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">int</span> <span class="kw4">raise</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">int</span> <span class="kw4">signal</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>
raise() 向程序发送特定的信号。一些信号：

</p>
<div class="table sectionedit2"><table class="inline">
	<tr class="row0">
		<th class="col0">信号</th><th class="col1">意思</th>
	</tr>
	<tr class="row1">
		<td class="col0">SIGABRT </td><td class="col1">终止错误</td>
	</tr>
	<tr class="row2">
		<td class="col0 leftalign">SIGFPE  </td><td class="col1">浮点指针错误</td>
	</tr>
	<tr class="row3">
		<td class="col0 leftalign">SIGILL  </td><td class="col1">失效指令</td>
	</tr>
	<tr class="row4">
		<td class="col0 leftalign">SIGINT  </td><td class="col1">用户输入 CTRL-C</td>
	</tr>
	<tr class="row5">
		<td class="col0">SIGSEGV </td><td class="col1">非法内存存取</td>
	</tr>
	<tr class="row6">
		<td class="col0">SIGTERM </td><td class="col1">终止程序</td>
	</tr>
</table></div>
<!-- EDIT2 TABLE [156-334] -->
<p>

成功时返回零，而失败时返回非零值。
</p>

<p>
相关主题： <a href="signal" class="wikilink1" title="cn:c:other:signal">signal</a>
</p>

</div>
